          h2 What's Node
          hr
          img(src="/images/node/node-under-hood.png")
          p A platform that makes writing powerful C/C++ server-side apps easy by essentially wrapping them in JavaScript.
      div#why-node.step.slide(data-x="1800", data-y="-1100", data-scale="1", data-rotate="60")
        h2 
          b Why Node
        hr
        ul
          li It's JavaScript!
          li Savings in I/O cost
          li Savings in Memory
      div#async-io.step.slide(data-x="2000", data-y="0", data-scale="1", data-rotate="90")
        img(src="/images/node/two_approaches_to_IO.jpeg")
