        h2
          b How to be so fast?
        hr
        ul
          li single thread
          li V8 JavaScript engine
          li non-blocking I/O
          li event driven (event-loop)
      div#multi-thread.step.slide(data-x="1000", data-y="1800", data-rotate="150", data-z="-2000")
        h2 Multi-thread + Blocking I/O 
        img(width="100%",src="/images/node/multiThreadedServer.png")
