        h2 When to Use?
        hr
        ul
            li 1. Build a (soft) real-time social app like Twitter or a chat app.
            li 2. Build high-performance, high I/O, TCP apps like proxy servers, PaaS, databases, etc.
            li 3. Build backend logging and processing apps.
            li 4. Add a RESTful API-based web server in front of an application server.
